Vault code was originally done by Radix, Thane of Hoerk
If you wish to use it, read the comments in vault_room.c

In YOUR vault room, use these functions for various reasons:

set_save_file(string file)
   set an optional save file if you don't like the existing one
set_vault_log(string file)
   Sets an optional log file if you don't like the default
set_admins(string *people)
   Sets an array of player names  that are allowed to view the vault log

Radix
December 4, 1995
